tive treatment of Hawaiian mythology.With an introduction by Katherine Luomala.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertHawaii eBook Package Archive pre 2000z978311056415040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780824840716423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780824840716.jpg  a978-3-11-056415-0  Hawaii eBook Package Archive pre 2000b2000  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LT  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK